{"type": "article", "id": 21197, "title": "拜托大家，快点振作起来吧 丨好奇心研究所", "description": "躺在被窝里一个一个念叨一遍嗯。", "date": "2016-01-24T08:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11405, "name": "好奇心研究所"}], "category": 5, "column": 33, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150255jyLEUNgw0XRGM9mp.gif", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>1. 气温。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150757Xi2nwb5up9ZDCNcY.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"390\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.78\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>2. 买了过冬产品，</strong><strong>却因为严寒被耽误的快递。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150758J0RkfKWN1PtXdpmg.gif\" width=\"340\" height=\"232\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.68235294\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>3. 北京的空气/堵车/地铁人流/舒适度。至于房租能不能消沉会 = = 。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150801fgu4T3sID7tYavx9.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong>4. 关键时刻卡住的进度条。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150804NOzxhIEPpJaM5cng.jpg\" width=\"580\" height=\"379\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.65344828\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong>5. 审查。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150805lp5uQO6X0UgMsYnK.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"297\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong>6. 审美。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261508059S23g6wUxaVK0eGv.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"412\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.74909091\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong>7. 钱包。@TM</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150806uCvaEZlp3YB7tDLn.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"380\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.76\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong>8. 更近一点，年终奖。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150808lcht0wbrFJ4oaNB2.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.20648148\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong>9. 休刊超过 500 天的富坚义博。</strong><strong>@</strong><strong>半开窗棂听树上七日夏蝉</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072615081006TsYKQPEeVqU452.jpg\" width=\"387\" height=\"220\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56847545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong>10. 作为喜剧演员的邓超。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261508109ECDM8ntLiHXks3f.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"405\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong>11. 国产偶像剧，尤其是女主角。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150810hDLF0M7WosVEBtPO.jpg\" width=\"539\" height=\"319\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.59183673\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong>12. 今天打开电视看到的几乎所有国产动画片。曾经多好看啊！</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150811mRc1gCWbf06YGSEz.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong>13. 威廉王子的发际线。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150812uXa2AixM6lmdcBry.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"299\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong>14. 高四的同学们。@放空</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150815h6Szaup7siKnEQBf.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong>15. 假期的长度/质量。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150821LoQ5DZnzibltVK7J.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong>16. 外卖的丰富程度。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150824XTV2m73eu1oOhCWR.gif\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong>17. 我自己的，智商/颜值/胸/丁丁/ RP/期末成绩单，过年回家面对所有亲戚。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150827jAz5PCdIwxv70Jo2.gif\" width=\"320\" height=\"154\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.48125\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong><em>好奇心研究所的微博（@好奇心研究所）和微信公众号（ID：QLab42）全面上线啦，关注就可以与所长亲密接触。</em></strong> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}